During the {{ill|Jingō-keiun|ja|神護景雲|12=draft}} era (769 CE), during the {{ill|Usa Hachiman Oracle Incident|ja|宇佐八幡宮神託事件|12=draft}}, the priestess {{ill|Karashima no Suguri Yosome|ja|辛嶋勝与曽女|12=draft}} received an oracle from the Hachiman deity and refused twice to hear the imperial decree read by {{ill|Wake no Kiyomaro|ja|和気清麻呂|12=draft}}, the envoy of {{ill|Empress Shōtoku|ja|称徳天皇|12=draft}}.<ref name="inuma" />

